<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Introduction - Data Privacy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<style>
    /* Special Content Blocks css */
    .definition-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(67, 97, 238, 0.1) 0%, rgba(72, 149, 239, 0.1) 100%);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .quote-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(247, 37, 133, 0.05) 0%, rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.05) 100%);
        border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        position: relative;
    }
    /* List Styles */
    .key-points {
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .key-points ul {
        list-style: none;
    }
    .key-points li {
        padding: 0.8rem 0 0.8rem 2.5rem;
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .key-points li:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 1.4rem;
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--primary-light);
    }
    .key-points .fa-icon {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 1rem;
        color: var(--primary-light);
        font-size: 1rem;
    }
    /* Footer Styles */
    footer {
        background: var(--dark);
        color: var(--white);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .navbar {
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .nav-container {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .nav-links {
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .nav-item {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .main-container {
            margin-top: 8rem;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        .content-card {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }
    }
    /* Reset */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background: #f9fafb;
        color: #121213;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    header {
        background-color: purple;
        padding: 0.0rem 0rem;
        color: #ecf0f1;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 100;
    }
    header h1 {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    nav {
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    nav ul {
        display: flex;
        list-style: none;
        gap: 1.8rem;
    }
    nav ul li a {
        color: #ecf0f1;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    nav ul li a:hover {
        background-color: #418dda;
    }
    main {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    main h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        color: #3e7ab7;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    main p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 700px;
    }
    main ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        color: #34495e;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    main ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }
    footer {
        margin-top: 0rem;
        background-color:purple;
        color: #ecf0f1;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0rem 0;
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 0px;
    }
</style>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
<%- include('partials/navbar', {currentPage: 'introduction'}); %>    </div>
  </header>

   <main class="container">
    <h2>Introduction to Data Privacy</h2>

    <div class="key-points">
      <ul>
        <li>In the 21st century, data privacy stands as a critical pillar of digital trust, decisively shaping how personal information is collected, processed, and secured (Kuye, 2023).</li>
        <li>With the explosive growth of data-driven technologies—ranging from social media to artificial intelligence—individuals and organizations are confronted with significant challenges in safeguarding sensitive data (Liu, 2018).</li>
        <li>According to Torre, Alferez, Soltana, Sabetzadeh, & Briand (2020), global regulatory frameworks like the GDPR and New Zealand's Privacy Act 2020 aim to harmonize innovation with ethical data practices.</li>
        <li>This project investigates the technical, legal, and strategic dimensions of data privacy to provide actionable solutions for stakeholders.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

   
  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Data Privacy. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>